# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Pi Lesson Extractor — environment configuration
#
# Copy to `.env` and fill in the provider you want to use:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# Only ONE provider is required. The provider is auto-detected from the model
# name, or set LLM_PROVIDER explicitly. The same model is used for both the
# per-session review and the AGENTS.md proposal unless you override AGENTS_*.
#
# ⚠️ Only AWS Bedrock (below) has been tested. The OpenAI / Anthropic / Google
#    provider configs are wired up but UNTESTED — treat them as a starting point.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── AWS Bedrock (Claude via Bedrock) — DEFAULT / TESTED ──────────────────────
LLM_PROVIDER=bedrock
REVIEW_MODEL=us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0
AGENTS_MODEL=us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0
AWS_REGION=us-east-1
# Credentials: either set explicit keys here, or rely on the AWS default
# credential chain (profiles, SSO, instance roles).
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=...
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=...
# AWS_SESSION_TOKEN=...

# Optional tuning (apply to any provider)
# AGENTS_MAX_TOKENS=8192      # output budget for the proposal (default 32000)
# AGENTS_TEMPERATURE=0.7
# REVIEW_TEMPERATURE=0.2

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Alternative providers below — UNTESTED. Comment out the Bedrock block above
# and uncomment one of these to try them.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── OpenAI (UNTESTED) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LLM_PROVIDER=openai
# REVIEW_MODEL=gpt-5.5
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# ── Anthropic, direct API (UNTESTED) ─────────────────────────────────────────
# LLM_PROVIDER=anthropic
# REVIEW_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── Google Gemini (UNTESTED) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LLM_PROVIDER=google
# REVIEW_MODEL=gemini-3.1-pro
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=...

# ── Misc ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PORT=3001                   # backend port
# REVIEW_CACHE_DIR=.review-cache
